# If set, the demo will use remote storage via JSON-RPC instead of local SQLite.
# When unset/empty, a local wallet_*.db file is used.
#
# You can use either of these patterns:
#
# 1) Boolean / flag style (uses built-in Babbage URLs by network):
#    USE_REMOTE_STORAGE=true
#
# 2) URL style (recommended for local Go Storage Server or custom servers):
#    USE_REMOTE_STORAGE=http://localhost:8100
